Package: connectivity-test
Version: 1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), curl, iproute2, systemd
Maintainer: Kim Asplund <kim.asplund@gmail.com>
Description: Network Connectivity Test and Service Monitor
 This package installs a service that monitors network connectivity
 and local services, with the ability to restart services and
 initiate system reboots if necessary.
